Package org.forgerock.opendj.maven.doc

Helps to build generated documentation sources.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandLineTool
    Represents a command-line tool as used in the configuration for GenerateRefEntriesMojo.
    DocsMessages
    This file contains localizable message descriptors having the resource name org.forgerock.opendj.maven.doc.docs.
    GenerateConfigurationReferenceMojo
    Generates the configuration reference, a set of HTML documents describing the server configuration.
    GenerateGlobalAcisTableMojo
    Generates documentation source table listing global ACIs.
    GenerateMessageFileMojo
    Generates an XML file of log messages found in properties files.
    GenerateRefEntriesMojo
    Generate DocBook RefEntry source documents for command-line tools man pages.
    GenerateResultCodeDocMojo
    Generates documentation source for LDAP result codes based on org.forgerock.opendj.ldap.ResultCode.
    GenerateSchemaDocMojo
    Generate schema-related reference documentation sources.
    Utils
    Provides utility methods for generating documentation.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GenerateRefEntriesMojo.Mode
    Represents the execution mode of this plugin.
